{"tid":42561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日好多手汗？","createTime":"2016-12-16T18:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T10:55:27.000Z","uid":16686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b2ff3d65c42767d870f1fa9c5d187a97367ec6","tid":42561,"uid":16686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:38:49.000Z","msg":"由細到大都勁多手腳汗<br />\n成日搞到周圍濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩方法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd29a94a343da2de59871dd177d05a96a14c686","tid":42561,"uid":56614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都勁多手腳汗<br />\n成日搞到周圍濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩方法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前都好多 依加飲水多左 同埋食小啲辣野都好咗幾多 <br />\n最緊要唔好太緊張 放鬆心情就唔會出手汗<br />\n利申 個人經驗 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9633f22bad8f378bff49cd123b5d94911717791","tid":42561,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:00:11.000Z","msg":"有個fd係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻手好似有閃粉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effa0a4c3b358426ae6b6da99a517e2094a9ade3","tid":42561,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"088eb3f877b06de3cfadfbb66462d65c7b4e1553","tid":42561,"uid":5382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:01:06.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"7e7288ccbf3786d92864d74df74df1ca5d3f8dd1","tid":42561,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"手腳都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e02592d9e2e54fb3615d674f0c0eaf6952f3f","tid":42561,"uid":24526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"我啲手汗未至於滴水<br />\n但隻手長期濕潤 <br />\n好怕同人握手拖手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 中學果陣用部samsung電話<br />\n有次唔見電話 office啲阿姐問我咩牌子<br />\n我話samsung 個阿姐話無samsung 電話報失<br />\n後尾先發現背面logo都比我啲手汗捽溶咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個阿姐以為部電話牌子係anycall"},{"pid":"215bb98de3a8780b40c21a041a846799397961ac","tid":42561,"uid":2435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:09:22.000Z","msg":"我識人係咁 <br />\n隻手仲因爲咁成日痕<br />\n仲會生汗疹<br />\n其實有無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a94fb647f21e2577bfeac649ec4dc16ce5e631c","tid":42561,"uid":16686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手腳都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用iPhone 長期掃唔到指紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433271645da6f0c111b40b22b8c90256dd1cc6f6","tid":42561,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手腳都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用iPhone 長期掃唔到指紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明唔緊張，啲汗都滲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f9f4b8986cdff20a917ad6144b48ef91969d3f","tid":42561,"uid":16979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手腳都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用iPhone 長期掃唔到指紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2788635ab39aea236357e0e16312208240e3ebbc","tid":42561,"uid":16686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>手腳都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用iPhone 長期掃唔到指紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘係啲汗抺唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}